titles.title: CB 144 My Soul Doth magnify the Lord

verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
MY SOUL DOTH MAGNIFY THE LORD,
And my spirit hath rejoiced in God my Savior,
For He that is mighty hath done great things,
And holy is His name.
